{"tid":2236821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第四波爆疫港大專家促盡快封高危場所 預警第五波聖誕新年殺到","createTime":"2020-10-09T18:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T00:58:46.000Z","uid":29627,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"828f3cce43dc9107db162db33af51b3bb1ade71c","tid":2236821,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:22:19.000Z","msg":"第四波爆疫港大專家促盡快封高危場所 預警第五波聖誕新年殺到<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xwvSrDiOANznRheosXyvnV2sBlc=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JG5JO7XFUZBZXPGZREJUZOPUJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxwvSrDiOANznRheosXyvnV2sBlc%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJG5JO7XFUZBZXPGZREJUZOPUJU.jpg&h=079a86c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港疫情惡化，上周已警告本港進入第四波疫情的香港大學公共衞生學院教授高本恩表示，第三波疫情後病毒沒有消失，9月底短暫本地個案零確診後回升，引發第四波疫情。他預料未來一至兩周確診個案持續上升，若政府盡快如下周一收緊社交距離措施，如關閉酒吧及卡拉OK等高危場所，確診個案或會於11月回落，第四波規模越小。市民要學會與病毒共存，當第四波疫情減退及放寬措施後，可能聖誕及農曆新年又有第五波，未來半年至一年本港會循環有多個小規模疫潮，直至有疫苗為止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/LDDY6XQWYBDK7NAW2ND4XVSSQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FLDDY6XQWYBDK7NAW2ND4XVSSQE%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=a3b795c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FLDDY6XQWYBDK7NAW2ND4XVSSQE%2F&h=7fda93f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/LDDY6XQWYBDK7NAW2ND4XVSSQE/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b36da84157ad2c7b490d964e7d6f3df646f5322","tid":2236821,"uid":26773,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:22:55.000Z","msg":"由.一月聽到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb529eab8379cc3314589274d7fd